  "instruction": "Count all .py files recursively under /tmp/code_proj/ and write only the integer count to ~/Desktop/py_count.txt (e.g. '5'). Then configure VS Code User Settings with these four keys: editor.fontSize=14, editor.lineHeight=24, editor.wordWrap='on', and files.trimTrailingWhitespace=true. Finally, open https://docs.python.org/ in a new Chrome tab.",
